In this section, we will look at how you complete the setup for your Oculus Rift HMD and peripherals.

[region:warning]
When you first plug your Oculus Rift into your PC, the Rift software may ask you to update the firmware for your Rift. DO NOT skip this or your Rift might not work with UE4!
[/region]

1. After the Rift drivers have finished installing the following screen will be displayed. 
    Press the **Next** button to begin the Rift setup process and follow the directions on the screen.

    ![](Rift_Setup_Screen_00.png)

[region:note]
If you need help during any part of the Rift setup process, click on the **Get Help** link that is in the lower lefthand corner to get help.
[/region]

